The,Kore,Real,Time,Messaging,API,is,used,to,create,applications,that,interact,with,users,in,real,time,This,API,uses,websockets,to,receive,messages,and,can,receive,events,from,the,Kore,Messaging,Platform,API,OAuth,is,used,for,authentication,Events,are,push,notifications,in,JSON,format,Kore,offers,a,streamlined,bot,based,enterprise,messaging,platform,with,security,that,complies,with,regulatory,mandates